name: Edcel Bar Gane
Lore: 'Senator from the planet Roona. One of the first to support Amidala''s motion for a vote of no confidence in Supreme Chancellor Valorum. Intolerant of other species.',
Text: 'Agenda: ambition. While in a senate majority, opponent may not draw more than one battle destiny in battles at battleground sites and you may not cancel opponent''s battle destiny draws at sites.',
